casebody.data:
N.B. D., Petitioner,
v.
KENTUCKY CABINET FOR HEALTH AND FAMILY SERVICES. No. 19-638 Supreme Court of the United States. January 13, 2020

Motion of Nelida Maribel Diaz Juarez for leave to intervene as petitioner granted. The Solicitor General is invited to file a brief in this case expressing the views of the United States.
